        <p><strong>💥 Demo Crews:</strong> 16 Gal — DEWALT DXV16PA (4.7★)</p>
        <p><strong>🔫 Painters:</strong> 6 Gal (quiet) — DEWALT STEALTHSONIC 6 Gal</p>
